data.name: Reddit Clone
data.description: A Reddit Clone built using React, Node.js, Express & MongoDB. This is a fullstack project which includes authentication, CRUD operations, upvoting, downvoting, commenting, nested comments, pagination, sorting, searching, etc.

data.name: Multiplatform Photo Compressor
data.description: A multiplatform photo compressor built using Tauri and Rust . Capable for changing time stamps, extractig preview images, compressing images, etc.

data.name: Customised C Shell
data.description: A customised C shell built using C. Capable of executing all the commands that a normal shell can execute. Also has some customised commands like pinfo, history, etc.
